items.title: Canadian wildfire smoke chokes Midwest as flood threat looms in Carolinas
items.description: A total of 1 to 4 inches of rain fell across the I-95 corridor on Thursday, leading to numerous flash flood warnings.

items.title: Trump unveils sweeping tariffs in 'new system of trade'
items.description: President Donald Trump signed an executive order Thursday, slapping tariffs on most of America's trading partners set to take effect next week.

items.title: WATCH:  Supersized stick insect discovered in Australia
